nodes.text: Catherine Munroe, known in the credits as Cathy Munro, is an actor who portrayed Zuckuss in Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back. Episode V was the first movie of her career. Though most notable for her appearance as the Gand bounty hunter, Munro also had a small role as the Snivvian Wiorkettle.
Munro is a close friend of actor Chris Parsons, who portrayed the droid 4-LOM.
